00:50:09,760 --> 00:50:13,280
even though they're going to be versus like, 
"Oh, [inaudible 00:50:12] let's roll this back."

548
00:50:13,280 --> 00:50:13,700
Yes.

549
00:50:13,700 --> 00:50:14,120
Okay.

